data.description:
THIS COULD BE YOURS! Wonderful opportunities await you including $5,000 in seller credit and the possibility of an Assumable FHA Loan with a 2.875% Interest rate or a 100% Financing Loan through participating lenders.
This Fantastic Family Home is For Sale in D'Iberville north of I-10. Features Include: Split and Open Floor Plan Concept (Floor Plan and Square Footage sketch attached), Smart Home Automation (doorbell, garage door, hallway lights, alarm, thermostat and front door entry), Newly Built in 2021, 4 Bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms, Updated and Move-In Ready, Fenced Yard, Refrigerator, Security System to Remain, Double Garage, Front and Back porches and close proximity to schools, shopping, sports complex, I-10 and Hwy 67.
Ask your favorite Realtor how you could become the new owner of this fabulous home!
